<sect1 id="IsLeapYear">
  <title>IsLeapYear</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">STD.Date.IsLeapYear<indexterm>
      <primary>STD.Date.IsLeapYear</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>Date.IsLeapYear</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>IsLeapYear</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis> <emphasis>ano</emphasis> <emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="80.50pt"/>

      <colspec/>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><emphasis>year</emphasis></entry>

          <entry>A year value in the INTEGER2 format.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:</entry>

          <entry>IsLeapYear retorna um valor BOOLEAN</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>A função <emphasis role="bold">IsLeapYear</emphasis> retorna TRUE se
  <emphasis>year</emphasis> é um ano bissexto no calendário gregoriano (ou
  gregoriano proléptico).</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting format="linespecific">IMPORT STD;
INTEGER2 MyYear := 2012;   //2012
  
D := STD.Date.IsLeapYear(MyYear);
    //D contains TRUE, 2012 is a leap year
  
  </programlisting>

  <para/>
</sect1>
